      <p>The Trails of Ceylon participates in various affiliate marketing programs, including but not limited to Amazon Associates, Booking.com, GetYourGuide, and other affiliate programmes.</p>
      <p>This means that when you click certain links on this website and make a purchase or booking, we may receive a commission. This commission comes at <strong>no additional cost to you</strong>.</p>
      <p>We only recommend products, services, and accommodation that we genuinely believe provide value to our readers. Our editorial opinions are not influenced by commercial relationships.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
